metadata.name: Rayhan
metadata.description:
A 13 years old girl, on a terrible night lost her whole family cause of the earthquake... 
She got a huge shock but didn't give up, after years of deep depression she found her way during her therapies... 
Now after 20 years she is a great psychologist, now she helps others with their loss and the big shocks of losing our beloved ones.

Digital painting mixed with hand-drawn doodles
